	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64117487"><p>Three words make your suggestion useless:</p><p>Inverse. Square. Law.</p><p>The further away from Earth you get, the more spread out the beam will eventually be when it hits Earth. Instead of hitting the receiver you scorch the entire city it's in.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64117487">

