		<div id="comment_body_64118047"><p><div class="quote"><p>Wouldn't extra sunlight cause more climate change?</p></div><p>Not enough to notice. Turns out the heating due to the greenhouse effect from burning fossil fuel is much much larger than the waste heat of the energy production. We'd need to expand energy use by many orders of magnitude before the actual waste heat would be a problem.</p></div>
